{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "1073/2025", "authoritative_decision_date": "26/03/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "刑事訴訟程序的上訴", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-0fd94a44268b1df0.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42367", "source_chunk_ids": ["1073_2025_zh_c0000_dd8e83d319c0", "1073_2025_zh_c0001_e21a6543ba1a", "1073_2025_zh_c0002_84cad33cb919", "1073_2025_zh_c0003_a9bd62eca1ae", "1073_2025_zh_c0004_4b9ad7471499", "1073_2025_zh_c0005_273ecdcf83f5", "1073_2025_zh_c0006_c43c710c20ef", "1073_2025_zh_c0007_b313052be73f", "1073_2025_zh_c0008_c9721d41e28e", "1073_2025_zh_c0009_ca6fe7d05b6c", "1073_2025_zh_c0010_e4525371db8c", "1073_2025_zh_c0011_3b23f015a5d1", "1073_2025_zh_c0012_041334cf39d9"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/1073_2025/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/1073_2025/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "澳門特別行政區檢察院指控嫌犯A以直接正犯及既遂的方式觸犯《道路交通法》第89條所規定及處罰的一項「逃避責任罪」。原審法院判決嫌犯A被控以直接正犯、既遂的方式1觸犯一項由第3/2007號法律《道路交通法》第89條所規定及處罰的「逃避責任罪」，罪名成立，判處102日罰金，罰金之日額定為120澳門元，即合共12,240澳門元。此外，原審法院判決嫌犯A禁止駕駛，為期七個月。本上訴案涉及審查證據錯誤、量刑過重及逃避責任罪的問題。", "holding": "本上訴案裁定上訴人A的上訴理由部分成立，因此改判上訴人75日的罰金，每日120澳門元，合共9,000澳門元。維持原審法院對上訴人所科處的禁止駕駛為期七個月的附加刑。", "legal_basis": ["《刑事訴訟法典》第114條", "《刑法典》第47條第1款", "《道路交通法》第89條及第94條"], "disputed_issues": ["審查證據錯誤", "量刑過重", "逃避責任罪"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
{"core_case_metadata": {"authoritative_case_number": "1087/2025/A", "authoritative_decision_date": "12/02/2026", "court": "澳門法院", "language": "zh", "case_type": "效力之中止", "pdf_url": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh-02f1ffc676bdda1f.pdf", "text_url_or_action": "https://www.court.gov.mo/sentence/zh/42147", "source_chunk_ids": ["1087_2025_A_zh_c0000_c840e2fb9767", "1087_2025_A_zh_c0001_ef47f402bc14", "1087_2025_A_zh_c0002_77723d065de5", "1087_2025_A_zh_c0003_ebd611185a92", "1087_2025_A_zh_c0004_d4acfa039db3"], "source_case_paths": ["cases/zh/2026/1087_2025_a/full_text.txt", "cases/zh/2026/1087_2025_a/metadata.json"]}, "generated_digest_metadata": {"case_summary": "本案件涉及保安司司長宣告聲請人於2009年11月6日獲批的居留許可無效的行政行為。聲請人請求中止該行政行為效力，但被聲請實體及檢察院認為不符合《行政訴訟法典》第120條及第121條第1款規定的要件。", "holding": "本院合議庭不批准是次中止行政行為效力的聲請。", "legal_basis": ["《行政訴訟法典》第120條", "《行政訴訟法典》第121條第1款"], "disputed_issues": ["難以彌補之損失的要件是否已符合", "中止行政行為效力不會嚴重侵害該行為在具體情況下所謀求之公共利益", "卷宗內無強烈跡象顯示司法上訴屬違法"]}, "generation_status": "local_model_generated", "generation_method": "local_model_generated", "model_name": "qwen2.5:3b-instruct", "prompt_version": "day45_prompt_b_tch_norm", "script_normalization_applied": false, "output_script": "traditional_chinese", "provenance_notes": ["Local-only generation path.", "No cloud API/database used.", "backend=ollama_cli"]}
